title: Deus Ex Machina
content:
Welcome to the latest episode of Rookies!

Rookies is an animated sketch comedy about a group of clone recruits who work at the SCP Foundation, causing havoc and mayhem on the job.

**Episode 10 - Deus Ex Machina**

Finally, the origins of the clone recruits is revealed!

Inspired by [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-2000 SCP-2000 (Deus Ex Machina) by HammerMaiden].
